We recommended that the:

Local Chief Executive instruct the Human Resource Management Officer (HRMO) to  see to it that the work to be performed by job order personnel is in accordance with their job description or duties and responsibilities stated in their contract;

Municipal Accountant and HRMO check the completeness of required supporting documents to establish the validity and propriety of payments made to job order/service contract personnel.
